author: Jack Power
title: Coronavirus: HSE investigating incorrect text messages about test results
description: Backlog of tests stands at 11,000 but should be cleared by end of week, HSE chief says
content:
The Health Service Executive (HSE) is investigating an issue where people have been incorrectly informed their test for coronavirus was negative, when in fact they had contracted the virus.
